Title: Part 13: The Witchking
Text: I found the Rohirrim and just arrived in time!The enemy got also support.. from the evil mens of the east and south. They brought giant Mumakils into the battle. A fight the Rohirrim can't win alone! I will help them by killing all the leaders on top and the Witchking himself with the help of Eowyn and Merry!
CompleteText: The Witchking and the Easterling leaders are dead! Now we should win this battle!I should talk to Gandalf in Minas Tirith next.
